短。人类和恶魔之间建立了绝对的信赖关系。不过，罗赛特的生命能够维持到和弟弟尤休亚相见么？","name":"クロノクルセイド","name_cn":"圣枪修女","tags":[{"name":"GONZO","count":325,"total_cont":0},{"name":"圣枪修女","count":291,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2003","count":183,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":181,"total_cont":0},{"name":"主角不灭反定律","count":130,"total_cont":0},{"name":"神结局","count":124,"total_cont":0},{"name":"石田彰","count":96,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":90,"total_cont":0},{"name":"宿命感","count":79,"total_cont":0},{"name":"治愈","count":73,"total_cont":0},{"name":"契约","count":63,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫改","count":42,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奇幻","count":35,"total_cont":0},{"name":"BE","count":33,"total_cont":0},{"name":"圣职","count":29,"total_cont":0},{"name":"战斗","count":27,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":21,"total_cont":0},{"name":"永生","count":21,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2003年11月","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"クロノクルセイド","count":15,"total_cont":0},{"name":"紅優","count":12,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2003年","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"森山大輔","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2003年10月","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"催泪","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"川上とも子","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"积极","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"听说挺好","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"千葉紗子","count":5,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"圣枪修女"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"CHRNO CRUSADE"},{"v":"CHRONO CRUSADE"}]},{"key":"话数","value":"24"},{"key":"放送开始","value":"2003年11月24日"},{"key":"放送星期","value":"星期一、星期三（19话起）"},{"key":"官方网站","value":"http://www.fujitv.co.jp/b_hp/chrono/index.html"},{"key":"播放电视台","value":"フジテレビ"},{"key":"播放结束","value":"2004年6月9日"},{"key":"导演","value":"紅優（森川滋）"},{"key":"音乐","value":"七瀬光（伊藤真澄）"},{"key":"Copyright","value":"©福音弾"},{"key":"原作","value":"森山大輔"},{"key":"企画","value":"安田猛、小川洋、鈴木径男、酒匂暢彦、石川真一郎"},{"key":"系列构成","value":"冨岡淳広"},{"key":"脚本","value":"冨岡淳広、吉村清子、高橋ナツコ、ほそのゆうじ"},{"key":"分镜","value":"紅優（森川滋）、神戸洋行、加藤敏幸、阿部達也、川瀬敏文、中山勝一、佐山聖子、石踊宏、鵜飼ゆうき